1
00:01:38,184 --> 00:01:42,440
[Episode 1]

2
00:01:42,440 --> 00:01:46,984
[Previous Review]
[Luoyang]

3
00:01:47,920 --> 00:01:52,079
If you don't agree to the marriage,
you won't get the Zixi pill.

4
00:01:52,079 --> 00:01:56,840
As long as mother can recover,
I am willing to do anything.

5
00:01:56,840 --> 00:02:00,000
Bow before the mirror.

6
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:05,000
Husband and wife are one, perpetual bliss endures.

7
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:11,040
Being forced to marry you
is the greatest humiliation of my life.

8
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:15,240
Today, you need to go to Fuyun Temple to pray.

9
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:19,120
If you are not sincere,
the prayers will be ineffective.

10
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:25,800
Young Madam, remember to kneel for ten hours.
Do not rise until the hour of You arrives.

11
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:29,759
How bold! How dare you try to deceive me
in the Grand Celestial Master Hall.

12
00:02:29,759 --> 00:02:32,719
Greetings, Floral Envoy.

13
00:02:33,759 --> 00:02:35,679
Greetings to you all.

14
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:39,784
Do not try to get the tribute medicine again.

15
00:02:39,784 --> 00:02:44,360
We must not let Madam He discover
that we gave her a counterfeit back then.

16
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:47,560
If I had discovered
that the Zixi pill was a counterfeit,

17
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:51,319
my mother wouldn't have passed away.

18
00:02:51,319 --> 00:02:53,599
My lady, go to the shop. I am stopping them here.

19
00:02:53,599 --> 00:02:54,639
Move!

20
00:02:54,639 --> 00:02:56,559
My lady.

21
00:02:57,960 --> 00:03:01,040
Someone fell in the water. Save her!

22
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:10,280
Yu Lu, let's go home.

23
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:14,520
I never had my heart set on Liu Chang.

24
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:18,280
If you wish to do this,
you must act swiftly and decisively.

25
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:26,520
Please witness for me and approve my divorce.

26
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:29,719
Part ways and find happiness separately.

27
00:03:29,719 --> 00:03:32,439
It is a beautiful story.

28
00:03:33,319 --> 00:03:36,640
This matter is concluded. Court dismissed.

29
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:44,479
Your Highness, I have never been your enemy.
This is a win-win strategy.

30
00:03:44,479 --> 00:03:49,639
I am just a woman who wishes
to hold her fate in her own hands.

31
00:03:49,639 --> 00:03:50,840
But she is too greedy,

32
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:53,560
insisting on taking the dowry
and even stirring up a lawsuit

33
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:55,159
to ruin the reputation of the Liu family.

34
00:03:55,159 --> 00:03:59,159
We cannot keep her alive.

35
00:03:59,159 --> 00:04:04,360
Mu Dan's escape at night is indeed disgraceful.

36
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:07,639
I will definitely establish myself in Chang'an.

37
00:04:07,639 --> 00:04:11,959
[Fragrance Garden]
I will reclaim Fragrance Garden on my own.

38
00:04:13,039 --> 00:04:16,399
Stop, He Wei Fang!

39
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:20,839
Floral Envoy?

40
00:04:20,839 --> 00:04:22,199
Don't you want
your decent household register anymore?

41
00:04:22,199 --> 00:04:24,759
You indeed manage the officials.

42
00:04:24,759 --> 00:04:29,400
I'm impressed by your capability and speed.

43
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:33,384
Jiang Xiao Hua, are you happy with it?

44
00:04:33,384 --> 00:04:34,959
[Jiang Xiao Hua]

45
00:04:34,959 --> 00:04:38,759
Yes.

46
00:04:38,759 --> 00:04:42,079
Genuine peonies for sale.
Each is blooming brightly.

47
00:04:42,079 --> 00:04:45,000
Anyone wishing to order, register here.
Complete your orders within three days.

48
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,079
- I will buy one.
- I will buy one.

49
00:04:46,079 --> 00:04:47,112
[Tailor Mu Dan incense powder as desired]
Okay.

50
00:04:47,112 --> 00:04:49,959
Custom-made, tailored fragrances.

51
00:04:49,959 --> 00:04:53,879
You can make your own fragrance.

52
00:04:53,879 --> 00:04:55,079
Take your handbasket.

53
00:04:55,079 --> 00:05:01,840
We weren't born on the same day,
but seek to get rich on the same day.

54
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:13,879
My house is not next
to the backyard of the Jiang Mansion,

55
00:05:13,879 --> 00:05:17,040
but exactly the backyard of the Jiang Mansion.

56
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:21,399
I invested money for you to do business,
yet haven't earned any profit.

57
00:05:21,399 --> 00:05:23,040
And you changed the house first?

58
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:27,976
Huamanzhu, grand opening.

59
00:05:27,976 --> 00:05:31,360
[Huamanzhu]

60
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:33,256
[Qingshuzhai]
We incorporate medicine into beauty products

61
00:05:33,256 --> 00:05:34,720
to enhance appearance and health.

62
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:38,240
Whatever you need, we have it all.

63
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:45,160
Jiang Chang Yang, when you're with the children,
you really don't seem like a corrupt official.

64
00:05:51,399 --> 00:05:55,920
Well, tell me, what kind of man do you fancy?

65
00:05:55,920 --> 00:06:00,879
I hope this person can understand me
better than I understand myself.

66
00:06:00,879 --> 00:06:06,959
Even if I say nothing, he knows
all my likes, dislikes, decisions, and dreams.

67
00:06:06,959 --> 00:06:11,519
No matter what situation I fall into,
he can face it with me.

68
00:06:11,519 --> 00:06:15,439
In the countless nights in our lives,
only the bright moon remains by our side.

69
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:18,100
Today I lend it to you.

70
00:06:18,100 --> 00:06:21,120
No matter where you are,

71
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:25,119
as long as you see it,
you will no longer be alone.

72
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:30,119
You should wipe the honey off your lips first.

73
00:06:42,319 --> 00:06:45,600
- Jingzhao Prefecture disregards the law,
- Six.

74
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:47,639
killing for money.

75
00:06:47,639 --> 00:06:51,519
Why has Huamanzhu become yours, where is Mu Dan?

76
00:06:51,519 --> 00:06:55,680
Mu Dan treated you so well,
why did you betray her?

77
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:57,920
I did not.

78
00:06:59,199 --> 00:07:04,519
Despite breaking the sworn oath,
I must sever my ties with you.

79
00:07:04,519 --> 00:07:08,759
From now on, you and I are no longer related.

80
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:17,119
Sheng Yi, if you are not doing well, come back.

81
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:24,360
May all your friends in the future
be intimate and sincere,

82
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:29,560
and never encounter people like me again.

83
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:31,759
Sheng Yi!

84
00:07:31,759 --> 00:07:35,560
- Sheng Yi!
- Sheng Yi!

85
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:37,360
Sheng Yi!

86
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:43,680
Mother, Yu Lu, did you see that?

87
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:45,840
- Make way!
- Make way!

88
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:49,759
I've heard Huamanzhu's cosmetic items
are highly praised.

89
00:07:49,759 --> 00:07:54,120
County Princess Ji An invites you to bring them
and go to Xingqing Palace immediately,

90
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:56,200
letting the nobles try them out.

91
00:08:02,216 --> 00:08:07,519
She's just a slave, yet you
tried every mean to defend her,

92
00:08:07,519 --> 00:08:09,680
ignoring our past friendship?

93
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:13,680
What Lady Li wants is Zi Shu's affection.

94
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:16,920
If I married He Wei Fang,
ending Zi Shu's affection of her,

95
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:19,600
it would help Lady Li solve her major concern.

96
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:24,970
The position of Deputy Transport Officer's vacant,
and His Majesty asked me to recommend talents.

97
00:08:24,970 --> 00:08:28,439
I thought to ask Your Highness
to help me pick some.

98
00:08:28,439 --> 00:08:33,399
But if this marriage is ruined,
I'm afraid the reward will be gone.

99
00:08:33,399 --> 00:08:39,919
You Zhen was harmed by your former lover,
fearing she may never bear children again.

100
00:08:39,919 --> 00:08:44,359
Your Highness wants me to marry into your family?

101
00:08:50,799 --> 00:08:57,279
If you don't despise my cripple, I am willing
to marry into the Prince Ning's Mansion.

102
00:08:57,279 --> 00:09:01,799
You and I will be together forever.

103
00:09:01,799 --> 00:09:06,879
I felt familiar with Mu Dan
once I saw her at the Liu Mansion in Luoyang.

104
00:09:06,879 --> 00:09:10,200
Over time, I developed affection to her.

105
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:13,240
Grilling wine in the pavilion,
drinking joyfully every night.

106
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:18,408
This affection was not born overnight,
but developed over time.

107
00:09:18,408 --> 00:09:19,440
[Fragrance Garden]

108
00:09:19,440 --> 00:09:24,200
Throughout the four seasons,
the garden heralds a new year.

109
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:27,839
Fragrance Garden opens today.

110
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:40,360
Fu, yours.

111
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:42,279
So many!

112
00:09:42,279 --> 00:09:43,279
Hers are so many.

113
00:09:43,279 --> 00:09:44,399
Ms. Sun, yours.

114
00:09:44,399 --> 00:09:46,159
- Thank you.
- Where's mine?

115
00:09:46,159 --> 00:09:47,960
This is Madam Tang's.

116
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:49,519
- A Man's.
- Thank you.

117
00:09:49,519 --> 00:09:50,720
You all have yours.

118
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:52,919
So heavy.

119
00:09:52,919 --> 00:09:54,639
How much do you get?

120
00:09:54,639 --> 00:09:56,439
More than yours.

121
00:09:57,360 --> 00:10:02,159
Everyone, since the Fragrance Garden opened,
our business has been prosperous.

122
00:10:02,159 --> 00:10:03,519
Thank you for your hard work.

123
00:10:03,519 --> 00:10:06,519
Today, just enjoy the food and wine.

124
00:10:06,519 --> 00:10:09,120
- Here.
- Thank you.

125
00:10:11,919 --> 00:10:13,719
One more, please.

126
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:19,200
Mu Dan, drinking is harmful to your health.

127
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:23,480
Mu Dan, you've been busy all day long.
Better have this pot of calming tea I made.

128
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:25,519
Mu Dan loves to drink.

129
00:10:25,519 --> 00:10:29,120
Today is joyful. A few cups won't hurt.

130
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:30,120
Come on.

131
00:10:30,120 --> 00:10:31,919
Eat it. It smells good.

132
00:10:31,919 --> 00:10:33,039
Try it.

133
00:10:33,039 --> 00:10:37,159
These are the pastries
made by you, right? I'll give it a try.

134
00:10:37,159 --> 00:10:40,200
Look, the shopkeeper
has prepared so much food for us.

135
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:44,000
Your skills have indeed improved.

136
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:47,336
Liu Lang, make some more for everyone to try.

137
00:10:47,336 --> 00:10:49,920
- Alright.
- Go ahead.

138
00:10:51,759 --> 00:10:57,080
You are getting better at coaxing kids.
Mr. Wu really taught you much.

139
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:58,960
I wasn't coaxing him.

140
00:10:58,960 --> 00:11:02,320
Liu Lang's skills have gotten better and better.

141
00:11:02,320 --> 00:11:06,840
I want to invite a pastry cook
from Shangao Pastry Shop to give us some advice,

142
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:10,760
so we can make a set of flower-themed pastries
to sell at the Fragrance Garden.

143
00:11:12,399 --> 00:11:15,919
Then I have to try them
to see if they're as you say.

144
00:11:15,919 --> 00:11:19,160
Save some for others. You eat later.

145
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:32,319
It will take some time. Honey, have a piece.

146
00:11:37,399 --> 00:11:39,199
Indeed, it's good.

147
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:45,639
Everyone, enjoy. Come with me.

148
00:11:45,639 --> 00:11:47,439
I'll try it.

149
00:11:48,919 --> 00:11:51,840
I have things to discuss with everyone later.

150
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:56,280
I might have to stay overnight.
Why don't you leave first?

151
00:11:57,399 --> 00:12:03,000
Everyone is watching. I can't leave before you.

152
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:06,720
With you here, they feel constrained.

153
00:12:06,720 --> 00:12:09,719
Just go. I'll explain for you.

154
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:19,879
Then I will leave first.

155
00:12:19,879 --> 00:12:23,159
Honey, don't drink too much,

156
00:12:23,159 --> 00:12:28,079
or I will feel upset.

157
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:31,879
Got it, just go.

158
00:12:31,879 --> 00:12:33,440
- I'm leaving.
- Go.

159
00:12:33,440 --> 00:12:35,240
I'm really leaving.

160
00:12:38,480 --> 00:12:39,879
- Are you still eating?
- Tasty.

161
00:12:39,879 --> 00:12:40,879
I have it.

162
00:12:40,879 --> 00:12:42,679
Give it to them.

163
00:12:43,639 --> 00:12:46,519
Everyone, let's make another toast.

164
00:12:46,519 --> 00:12:48,559
Alright, let's make another toast.

165
00:12:48,559 --> 00:12:50,440
Come on, let's make another toast.

166
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:51,519
Enjoy drinking.

167
00:12:51,519 --> 00:12:53,599
Alright, enjoy.

168
00:12:55,519 --> 00:12:59,040
The shopkeeper kept us here,
is there anything she wants to tell us?

169
00:13:01,519 --> 00:13:06,880
Jin Niang, this is yours. Here, Gui.

170
00:13:09,399 --> 00:13:13,479
Tao, this is yours.

171
00:13:15,592 --> 00:13:19,000
[Release from servitude]

172
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:25,399
In these months, I've seen all of you
dedicating yourselves to Fragrance Garden.

173
00:13:25,399 --> 00:13:30,520
A few days ago, I went to the authorities
and have arranged your release from servitude.

174
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:35,840
You have been so kind to us.
How can we repay your kindness?

175
00:13:35,840 --> 00:13:38,200
What are you doing? Get up, get up.

176
00:13:38,200 --> 00:13:41,479
We are all one family. Don't talk about repayment.

177
00:13:53,159 --> 00:13:55,840
These are your indentures.

178
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:59,240
The past was bitter,
but the future will be better.

179
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:05,719
From now on, you are no longer servants,
but are free people.

180
00:14:25,720 --> 00:14:30,320
Madam, we found the missing
white jade pearl hairpin in her room.

181
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:34,719
Now that we caught her red-handed,
how do you plan to deal with her?

182
00:14:35,480 --> 00:14:38,840
I moved to live in Fragrance Garden long ago.
That house has been empty since then.

183
00:14:38,840 --> 00:14:42,199
What hairpin? I have never seen it.

184
00:14:43,120 --> 00:14:48,559
If you didn't steal it,
did Mu Dan steal it and hide it with you?

185
00:14:48,559 --> 00:14:50,080
Nonsense.

186
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:54,120
Anyway, if you didn't do it, then she did it,
or maybe both of you conspired.

187
00:14:54,120 --> 00:15:00,200
Go call Mr. Jiang. Let him see
what kind of person is sleeping beside him.

188
00:15:00,200 --> 00:15:02,000
Yes.

189
00:15:04,879 --> 00:15:07,320
I was told to marry Mr. Jiang by His Highness.

190
00:15:07,320 --> 00:15:11,840
Now that I caught you stealing,
I should deal with it for His Highness.

191
00:15:11,840 --> 00:15:14,399
You framed me. Mr. Jiang wouldn't believe you.

192
00:15:14,399 --> 00:15:18,639
You, a thief, how dare you to slander me!

193
00:15:18,639 --> 00:15:22,080
Slap her mouth a hundred times as punishment.

194
00:15:22,080 --> 00:15:23,080
Yes.

195
00:15:23,080 --> 00:15:26,000
I didn't do it. Let me go.

196
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:27,639
Let me go. Let go of me.

197
00:15:27,639 --> 00:15:31,040
Don't touch me. Let me go.

198
00:15:41,000 --> 00:15:44,480
I act with integrity. Come at me.

199
00:15:44,480 --> 00:15:49,639
If you dare to frame Mu Dan rashly,
there won't be just me bleeding in this room.

200
00:15:49,639 --> 00:15:51,959
Mr. Jiang, you must take a good look.

201
00:15:53,559 --> 00:15:58,479
You…

202
00:15:59,320 --> 00:16:04,759
Mr. Jiang, you're finally here.
Mu Dan's people stole my jewelry.

203
00:16:04,759 --> 00:16:08,840
I was merely asking a few questions
and she even attacked me.

204
00:16:08,840 --> 00:16:11,759
I am hurt and so scared.

205
00:16:11,759 --> 00:16:14,200
I didn't. You are just making things up.

206
00:16:14,200 --> 00:16:16,904
- Fu.
- It's you…

207
00:16:28,919 --> 00:16:34,480
That's it. Mr. Jiang,
do you believe in Lian Zhou's word?

208
00:16:34,480 --> 00:16:36,280
Lian Zhou…

209
00:16:37,240 --> 00:16:38,720
Of course not.

210
00:16:38,720 --> 00:16:42,879
It's my fault that you're caught
in such a situation, I am…

211
00:16:42,879 --> 00:16:44,759
It's nothing, just a wound.

212
00:16:44,759 --> 00:16:47,040
You sit down.

213
00:16:48,039 --> 00:16:52,240
I'm fine, as long as you believe in Mu Dan.

214
00:16:52,240 --> 00:16:53,240
If you don't believe me…

215
00:16:53,240 --> 00:16:57,439
Sit down. Can you take care of yourself first?

216
00:17:00,360 --> 00:17:03,480
Your body is inherited from your parents.

217
00:17:03,480 --> 00:17:07,040
If your mother knew about this,
she would be heartbroken.

218
00:17:08,119 --> 00:17:12,720
Right. I need to stay here until I'm better.

219
00:17:15,119 --> 00:17:16,919
Be nicer.

220
00:17:18,160 --> 00:17:22,559
Chuan Yu, you are good to Fu,
even more attentive than to your master.

221
00:17:22,559 --> 00:17:26,440
I've hurt my back, but you didn't care at all.

222
00:17:26,440 --> 00:17:29,640
Naturally, the one
who caused your back injury should care.

223
00:17:29,640 --> 00:17:33,000
- Fu, Fu.
- Mu Dan.

224
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:34,720
Fu, let me see where you're hurt.

225
00:17:34,720 --> 00:17:35,720
Here.

226
00:17:35,720 --> 00:17:37,720
Has the physician been here? Will it leave a scar?

227
00:17:37,720 --> 00:17:41,480
It's alright, I don't care about it at all.

228
00:17:41,480 --> 00:17:45,119
Mr. Jiang has checked it, and gave me
the imperial medicine. Don't worry.

229
00:17:45,119 --> 00:17:47,400
With such an injury, how can you still smile?

230
00:17:47,400 --> 00:17:48,680
Just a little.

231
00:17:48,680 --> 00:17:52,960
Dou Jin told you everything
before you arrived here, right?

232
00:17:55,240 --> 00:17:59,000
Don't worry, Chuan Yu has applied medicine for me.

233
00:17:59,000 --> 00:18:02,000
Go check on Mr. Jiang's back injury.

234
00:18:03,839 --> 00:18:06,319
Your back got injured by Lian Zhou?

235
00:18:06,319 --> 00:18:10,359
No, it has nothing to do with today.

236
00:18:21,640 --> 00:18:24,800
Chuan Yu, please take good care of Fu for me.

237
00:18:27,440 --> 00:18:30,440
Honey, come with me.

238
00:18:45,079 --> 00:18:48,159
I have something to tell you.

239
00:18:49,119 --> 00:18:52,960
Well, Lian Zhou is here because of me.

240
00:18:52,960 --> 00:18:57,079
I'm sorry for that. I'm willing
to cooperate with you in acting.

241
00:18:57,079 --> 00:19:00,920
But this has nothing to do with Fu.

242
00:19:00,920 --> 00:19:05,680
Now, Lian Zhou treats Fu this way,
slandering her and punishing her.

243
00:19:05,680 --> 00:19:08,680
I must seek justice for Fu.

244
00:19:08,680 --> 00:19:09,880
If you want to stop me…

245
00:19:09,880 --> 00:19:17,359
Why would I? Tell me whatever you need me to do.

246
00:19:19,960 --> 00:19:25,079
No need for that. Thank you.

247
00:19:29,119 --> 00:19:33,240
You injured your back
when you carried me back that night?

248
00:19:34,559 --> 00:19:39,359
You remember that night?

249
00:19:39,359 --> 00:19:43,159
I was drunk, not dead. Of course, I remember.

250
00:19:44,240 --> 00:19:48,159
I just drank a bit too much,
and only remember a little.

251
00:19:49,880 --> 00:19:55,839
A little is enough. Then you'll pay
the cost of treating the back injury.

252
00:20:01,799 --> 00:20:03,279
Did they have a quarrel?

253
00:20:03,279 --> 00:20:06,039
The door was closed, and no sound came out,

254
00:20:06,039 --> 00:20:09,160
but I saw He Wei Fang return
to her courtyard with a stern face.

255
00:20:09,160 --> 00:20:10,359
Once she left,

256
00:20:10,359 --> 00:20:15,160
Mr. Jiang sent someone to inform us
that he will rest in your room tonight.

257
00:20:15,160 --> 00:20:18,359
I knew it. Men are never single-minded.

258
00:20:18,359 --> 00:20:22,440
It seems the Jiang Mansion
will be exclusively for you.

259
00:20:22,440 --> 00:20:25,400
Add more petals to the water,
then light all the incense in the room.

260
00:20:25,400 --> 00:20:27,200
Yes.

261
00:20:43,079 --> 00:20:45,680
Quack physician, can't even cure a few rashes.

262
00:20:45,680 --> 00:20:48,000
Madam, these rashes have developed strangely.

263
00:20:48,000 --> 00:20:52,680
I heard that He Wei Fang understands
some pharmacology. Maybe she's behind this.

264
00:20:52,680 --> 00:20:56,879
Madam, when Mr. Jiang comes,
you must ask him to stand up for you.

265
00:20:59,000 --> 00:21:00,359
What time is it?

266
00:21:00,359 --> 00:21:02,319
It's the hour of Xu.

267
00:21:02,319 --> 00:21:08,319
If Mr. Jiang sees me like this now,
how can I win his favor?

268
00:21:13,720 --> 00:21:17,440
Go tell Mr. Jiang that I was very happy
to know that he comes,

269
00:21:17,440 --> 00:21:20,519
but I caught a chill while bathing,

270
00:21:20,519 --> 00:21:24,440
and I'm afraid of infecting him,
so please do not visit.

271
00:21:24,440 --> 00:21:28,440
Once I recover, I will go apologize to him.

272
00:21:28,440 --> 00:21:30,240
Yes.

273
00:21:38,400 --> 00:21:40,319
Madam, do you really want to do this?

274
00:21:40,319 --> 00:21:44,079
I have consulted several physicians,
and they all said they can't cure it.

275
00:21:44,079 --> 00:21:46,759
What else can I do but plead with her?

276
00:21:46,759 --> 00:21:48,599
What a humiliation.

277
00:21:48,599 --> 00:21:50,960
Haven't I endured enough humiliation already?

278
00:21:50,960 --> 00:21:53,119
What's the harm in enduring it one more?

279
00:21:53,119 --> 00:22:01,119
As long as I can recover my face, there will be
plenty of opportunities to deal with her.

280
00:22:09,440 --> 00:22:13,559
Mu Dan, could you please meet me?

281
00:22:17,200 --> 00:22:19,519
Mu Dan.

282
00:22:19,519 --> 00:22:22,440
Lian Zhou, what's the matter?

283
00:22:22,440 --> 00:22:28,599
After I bathed with flowers last night,
and I covered in itchy rashes somehow.

284
00:22:28,599 --> 00:22:33,160
I know you understand pharmacology,
could you please help me out?

285
00:22:33,160 --> 00:22:34,519
Unfortunately,

286
00:22:34,519 --> 00:22:38,920
I heard that Fu stole your jewelry,
and it's currently under investigation.

287
00:22:38,920 --> 00:22:42,400
Before there are any leads,
I have no time to deal with it.

288
00:22:42,400 --> 00:22:50,200
I-I've made a mistake. Lady Zhu Fu did not steal.

289
00:22:52,000 --> 00:22:55,519
In that case, then you falsely accused Fu.

290
00:22:55,519 --> 00:23:01,519
How would you compensate for the injury
on Fu's neck and the wrongs suffered?

291
00:23:01,519 --> 00:23:05,240
I will explain to the servants
and restore Lady Zhu Fu's innocence.

292
00:23:05,240 --> 00:23:09,880
That's what you should do.
How is that compensation?

293
00:23:09,880 --> 00:23:15,040
Slander deserves a hundred slaps.
This is what you said, right?

294
00:23:23,720 --> 00:23:27,800
Then please count them, Mu Dan, Zhu Fu.

295
00:23:34,720 --> 00:23:39,280
What trick did you use to make her come
and admit her mistake?

296
00:23:43,480 --> 00:23:47,440
Chun previously extracted
a lot of flower juice for making beauty pills.

297
00:23:47,440 --> 00:23:52,880
She discovered that mixing several types
of flower juices can cause the rashes.

298
00:23:52,880 --> 00:23:57,279
Though there's no danger to life,
it can damage one's appearance

299
00:23:57,279 --> 00:23:58,880
and cause unbearable itch.

300
00:23:58,880 --> 00:24:02,319
So I took some and put it in her bathtub.

301
00:24:12,400 --> 00:24:16,799
You framed her for theft,
and now you deserve what you did.

302
00:24:16,799 --> 00:24:21,480
You need to write a statement of apology
and put it in the hall to apologize to Zhu Fu.

303
00:24:24,359 --> 00:24:30,480
Okay, I'll write it later.
Mu Dan, can you give me the antidote recipe?

304
00:24:31,599 --> 00:24:34,319
I don't know your past,

305
00:24:34,319 --> 00:24:39,400
but I can tell that you didn't want
to marry into here.

306
00:24:39,400 --> 00:24:42,279
You must have your grievances and helplessness,

307
00:24:42,279 --> 00:24:45,759
so try to secure something
at the Jiang Mansion to rely on for a lifetime.

308
00:24:45,759 --> 00:24:48,680
It's reasonable, and I can understand it.

309
00:24:49,720 --> 00:24:55,200
I'm focused solely on business
and don't want to fight for anything with you.

310
00:24:55,200 --> 00:24:59,200
If you no longer harm
my close friends and relatives,

311
00:24:59,200 --> 00:25:03,000
we can still live in peace as we did before.

312
00:25:03,000 --> 00:25:09,159
Focused solely on business?
Don't you care about Mr. Jiang's affections?

313
00:25:10,640 --> 00:25:17,280
I mean Sui Zhi and I are mutually in love,
so I don't need to fight for anything.

314
00:25:18,039 --> 00:25:22,160
Instead of wasting time here,
you should treat yourself better.

315
00:25:22,160 --> 00:25:23,960
You!

316
00:25:27,599 --> 00:25:30,839
Don't get upset over a man
who doesn't care about you.

317
00:25:31,720 --> 00:25:37,480
The more you get mad,
the harder the rashes to subside.

318
00:25:37,480 --> 00:25:42,040
Temper justice with mercy.
You are truly something.

319
00:25:43,759 --> 00:25:50,200
The world is harsh for us women,
why employ tricks to harm each other?

320
00:25:51,400 --> 00:25:53,870
You are the adopted daughter of Prince Ning.

321
00:25:53,870 --> 00:25:58,839
Besides your beauty, you must
have other remarkable qualities.

322
00:25:58,839 --> 00:26:04,328
Is there nothing else you want to do
besides pleasing your husband?

323
00:26:10,824 --> 00:26:15,880
I have many exceptionally talented women here.
They have long escaped the inner chambers.

324
00:26:15,880 --> 00:26:21,119
Now, they are all enjoying their lives
in embroidery, gardening, making incense,

325
00:26:21,119 --> 00:26:23,240
and dressing up.

326
00:26:23,240 --> 00:26:29,720
If you're interested in gardening,
you can come visit my garden.

327
00:26:30,799 --> 00:26:36,480
You want me to grow flowers
and do business with you?

328
00:26:36,480 --> 00:26:38,680
Anything wrong with that?

329
00:26:39,519 --> 00:26:43,279
You are so strange, married to Floral Envoy,

330
00:26:43,279 --> 00:26:46,240
yet still working hard
to earn small amounts of money.

331
00:26:46,880 --> 00:26:52,960
I truly don't understand
why Mr. Jiang is so devoted to you.

332
00:26:54,799 --> 00:26:58,759
What's wrong with earning money?
Who would refuse money?

333
00:26:58,759 --> 00:27:03,160
Besides, he likes me for having such abilities.

334
00:27:03,160 --> 00:27:05,040
Don't be arrogant.

335
00:27:06,599 --> 00:27:09,960
Apply it three times a day,
and you'll be cured in seven days.

336
00:27:10,720 --> 00:27:14,599
Think about what I've told you today.

337
00:27:14,599 --> 00:27:18,359
If you figure it out, you can come to me anytime.

338
00:27:41,720 --> 00:27:43,160
I truly don't understand

339
00:27:43,160 --> 00:27:47,760
why Mr. Jiang is so devoted to you.

340
00:27:49,519 --> 00:27:53,960
We acted our play so well
that Lian Zhou would say that.

341
00:28:01,319 --> 00:28:03,520
Dusk.

342
00:28:04,968 --> 00:28:07,272
[Joyful]

343
00:28:07,880 --> 00:28:09,680
Oh no.

344
00:28:16,160 --> 00:28:19,040
Mr. Jiang, I toast to you.

345
00:28:26,160 --> 00:28:29,880
They all say the newly appointed
Deputy Transport Officer is strict and fair.

346
00:28:29,880 --> 00:28:31,759
Mr. Qi, you should drink less.

347
00:28:31,759 --> 00:28:36,800
If you come to work with the smell of alcohol
tomorrow, I'm afraid you'll get scolded.

348
00:28:37,599 --> 00:28:40,599
I didn't have much work before.

349
00:28:40,599 --> 00:28:44,039
Since Liu Chang came, he's being strict and fair,

350
00:28:44,039 --> 00:28:45,599
showing no mercy at all.

351
00:28:45,599 --> 00:28:49,640
We're so busy that we couldn't even take a break.

352
00:28:49,640 --> 00:28:53,519
Liu Chang is just Prince Ning's son-in-law,

353
00:28:53,519 --> 00:28:56,859
and a pedantic scholar from a humble background.

354
00:28:56,859 --> 00:28:59,039
What can he achieve?

355
00:28:59,039 --> 00:29:01,119
He really has high ambitions.

356
00:29:01,119 --> 00:29:04,559
Repairing docks and consolidating fleets.

357
00:29:04,559 --> 00:29:10,480
I think he won't stop
until he shows Prince Ning some achievement.

358
00:29:10,480 --> 00:29:15,519
Zi Shu is working so hard,
is he aiming for promotion or…?

359
00:29:15,519 --> 00:29:20,319
Who doesn't want a promotion?
But benefits must still be secured.

360
00:29:20,319 --> 00:29:27,160
Otherwise, Liu Chang's meager salary
cannot support noble Lady Li.

361
00:29:27,160 --> 00:29:32,119
Despite complaining,
you still diligently follow Zi Shu's lead.

362
00:29:32,119 --> 00:29:37,000
Mr. Qi, the jade pendant you're wearing today
is probably worth as much as a year's salary.

363
00:29:39,079 --> 00:29:41,309
It's better to share the joy than enjoy alone.

364
00:29:41,309 --> 00:29:43,839
With such a lucrative opportunity,

365
00:29:43,839 --> 00:29:47,799
Mr. Qi, why don't you come
to my mansion tomorrow and tell me?

366
00:29:47,799 --> 00:29:49,680
My pleasure.

367
00:29:55,119 --> 00:30:01,399
I think the jade at Mr. Jiang's waist
looks even better.

368
00:30:05,319 --> 00:30:08,440
A precious jade matches a beauty well.

369
00:30:08,440 --> 00:30:10,160
Thank you, Mr. Jiang.

370
00:30:10,160 --> 00:30:14,759
Wait, Mr. Jiang.
You promised to give me a bracelet.

371
00:30:14,759 --> 00:30:17,159
You must not be biased.

372
00:30:29,319 --> 00:30:37,319
It's late, just drinking isn't fun.
How about blowing out a few candles?

373
00:30:38,319 --> 00:30:44,200
What's the hurry on such a long night?
We haven't even finished enjoying the wine.

374
00:30:45,279 --> 00:30:50,760
Even if it's just a social,
he doesn't have to hold women like this.

375
00:30:53,839 --> 00:30:58,879
Lian Zhou believed it,
surely hasn't seen Jiang Chang Yang this way.

376
00:31:01,119 --> 00:31:05,480
I knew it. I almost got confused by Lian Zhou.

377
00:31:16,960 --> 00:31:21,079
Jiang Sui Zhi, it's this late at night.
Why don't you go home?

378
00:31:21,079 --> 00:31:25,240
If you want to drink, I can accompany you.

379
00:31:27,960 --> 00:31:32,440
You're busy with business, yet you
surprisingly had time to pick me up today.

380
00:31:32,440 --> 00:31:35,639
Then, of course, I should drink with you.

381
00:31:36,799 --> 00:31:41,119
Mr. Qi, pay attention
to the business we discussed.

382
00:31:41,119 --> 00:31:43,680
My beloved is picking me up, so I'm leaving.

383
00:31:43,680 --> 00:31:45,839
Sui Zhi, you…

384
00:31:45,839 --> 00:31:51,920
Recently, Huamanzhu
released new sachets. Have a try.

385
00:31:51,920 --> 00:31:54,960
The rouge scent from Huanyun Tower
is indeed too strong.

386
00:31:54,960 --> 00:31:56,400
If you have these sachets,

387
00:31:56,400 --> 00:32:03,000
when returning home, you can avoid
interrogation from wives and concubines, right?

388
00:32:03,000 --> 00:32:04,800
Farewell.

389
00:32:20,960 --> 00:32:22,440
What's going on?

390
00:32:22,440 --> 00:32:23,880
We agreed you'd come to rescue me
at the first quarter of the Xu hour,

391
00:32:23,880 --> 00:32:25,279
but you arrived at the third.

392
00:32:25,279 --> 00:32:28,240
If you were any later, the candles
in the room would have blown out.

393
00:32:29,039 --> 00:32:31,509
I got frightened by Lian Zhou.

394
00:32:31,509 --> 00:32:33,240
We acted too well,

395
00:32:33,240 --> 00:32:36,000
and Lian Zhou truly thinks you fall for me.

396
00:32:36,000 --> 00:32:41,519
She even told me a bunch of strange words.

397
00:32:41,519 --> 00:32:46,440
She should really see
your flirtatious behavior today.

398
00:32:48,119 --> 00:32:53,639
Just take what she said a joke.
You didn't take it seriously, did you?

399
00:32:57,519 --> 00:32:59,920
Of course, I didn't.

400
00:32:59,920 --> 00:33:02,519
Lian Zhou only sees how good you treat me,

401
00:33:02,519 --> 00:33:07,240
yet doesn't know that it is because
we have a life-and-death friendship.

402
00:33:07,920 --> 00:33:11,759
But it's understandable
that outsiders don't understand

403
00:33:11,759 --> 00:33:15,399
why a high-ranking official
treats a small merchant so well.

404
00:33:21,480 --> 00:33:26,380
Over the years, I've seen a lot
of intrigues in officialdom

405
00:33:26,380 --> 00:33:29,800
and the false pretenses between people.

406
00:33:30,480 --> 00:33:34,880
Someone as honest and open-minded
as you is really rare.

407
00:33:34,880 --> 00:33:38,280
Of course, I would treat you sincerely.

408
00:33:42,240 --> 00:33:47,119
Are you drunk? Why are you suddenly praising me?

409
00:33:47,119 --> 00:33:50,520
Making me feel quite embarrassed.

410
00:33:51,480 --> 00:33:54,759
You are this kind of person,
so you can receive others' kindness towards you.

411
00:33:54,759 --> 00:33:58,319
Moreover, you also treat me well.

412
00:33:59,119 --> 00:34:03,799
You said it's hard to find a soulmate.

413
00:34:03,799 --> 00:34:08,720
There's no need to always express gratitude,
it makes us seem distant.

414
00:34:11,400 --> 00:34:16,079
You treat me sincerely,
and I will never let you down as a soulmate.

415
00:34:16,079 --> 00:34:19,519
From now on, in my heart, besides Fu and Chun,

416
00:34:19,519 --> 00:34:22,760
you are my most important person.

417
00:34:22,760 --> 00:34:25,839
If you need help, just tell me.

418
00:34:27,480 --> 00:34:33,760
Jiang Xiao Hua, we are soulmates,
and I can only rank third in your heart?

419
00:34:34,440 --> 00:34:36,959
Naturally, besties are more important.

420
00:34:54,039 --> 00:34:58,519
Here, take the prescription to get the medicine.

421
00:34:58,519 --> 00:35:00,319
Okay, thanks.

422
00:35:06,039 --> 00:35:08,960
Have all the gifts from clients been returned?

423
00:35:08,960 --> 00:35:12,280
Ms. Luo, who came for a consultation last time,
embroidered this handkerchief to show gratitude.

424
00:35:12,280 --> 00:35:16,280
This isn't any precious item,
and with shopkeeper's name,

425
00:35:16,280 --> 00:35:18,359
so I decided to keep it.

426
00:35:21,800 --> 00:35:22,920
[High Medical Skills]

427
00:35:22,920 --> 00:35:27,360
Her eye condition just improved,
she shouldn't do such taxing things.

428
00:35:27,360 --> 00:35:30,439
When she comes,
I'll definitely give her a good talking to.

429
00:35:32,079 --> 00:35:34,239
Please call the next person.

430
00:35:34,239 --> 00:35:36,039
Yes.

431
00:35:46,039 --> 00:35:47,839
Father.

432
00:35:50,320 --> 00:35:52,039
Liu Lang, remember.

433
00:35:52,039 --> 00:35:56,319
Spring is not yet full,
and crops are already growing. That's Qin.

434
00:35:57,480 --> 00:36:00,359
I taught your sister like this too.

435
00:36:14,360 --> 00:36:19,119
Right, Liu Lang.
You're holding the brush wrong again.

436
00:36:19,119 --> 00:36:21,480
Hold the brush like this,

437
00:36:21,480 --> 00:36:24,719
only then will the strokes
in your writing be proper.

438
00:36:24,719 --> 00:36:27,519
See? Here, try again.

439
00:36:28,800 --> 00:36:31,000
Yes, combine these two.

440
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:34,519
Move this back. Okay, try it now.

441
00:36:36,079 --> 00:36:42,360
It's this feeling. Nice. Right.

442
00:36:42,360 --> 00:36:44,160
Go further down.

443
00:36:47,000 --> 00:36:48,800
Mu Dan.

444
00:36:51,079 --> 00:36:53,760
Why are you here at this hour? Continue.

445
00:36:53,760 --> 00:36:56,960
You've helped Consort Shu recuperate
for several months, and she has improved a lot.

446
00:36:56,960 --> 00:37:00,280
Before returning to the palace,
she asked me to give you this painting

447
00:37:00,280 --> 00:37:03,399
to thank you for your companionship
during this time.

448
00:37:04,719 --> 00:37:10,479
She paid me for those medicinal herbs
and supplies. Why is Consort Shu so polite?

449
00:37:17,679 --> 00:37:21,920
You often ride with Consort Shu.
Your polo skills must have improved a lot.

450
00:37:21,920 --> 00:37:25,719
That's natural, do you dare
to compete with me someday?

451
00:37:25,719 --> 00:37:29,360
How bold, do you dare to bet on it?

452
00:37:29,360 --> 00:37:33,280
Isn't the interest you've collected
from me enough? Want to swindle me for more?

453
00:37:33,280 --> 00:37:34,559
Don't even think about it.

454
00:37:34,559 --> 00:37:37,480
Consort Shu has given you her well-bred horse.

455
00:37:37,480 --> 00:37:40,640
With a fine horse, are you still afraid to lose?

456
00:37:42,440 --> 00:37:46,119
Consort Shu has never looked down on me
because of my rank.

457
00:37:46,119 --> 00:37:48,039
She treats me well.

458
00:37:49,599 --> 00:37:53,320
Now that she has returned, it's not
as comfortable as being in another palace.

459
00:37:53,320 --> 00:37:57,960
Could you persuade His Majesty
to visit her more often?

460
00:37:57,960 --> 00:38:00,559
At least let her see her child more often.

461
00:38:00,559 --> 00:38:03,079
Don't worry, Consort Shu has been away
from the palace for a long time.

462
00:38:03,079 --> 00:38:06,640
His Majesty also misses her greatly
and will surely treat her well.

463
00:38:07,440 --> 00:38:11,760
Mu Dan, I've written another character,
please check if it's correct.

464
00:38:14,519 --> 00:38:18,480
I've never taught you this character,
how did you learn it?

465
00:38:18,480 --> 00:38:22,239
I've been observing the plaque
of the Fragrant Garden,

466
00:38:22,239 --> 00:38:24,599
so I learn to write it.

467
00:38:24,599 --> 00:38:29,760
Liu Lang is smart.
I'll teach you another character then.

468
00:38:29,760 --> 00:38:31,560
The Garden in Fragrance Garden.

469
00:38:32,440 --> 00:38:34,240
Here.

470
00:38:44,119 --> 00:38:45,919
I'll write the outer part.

471
00:38:49,639 --> 00:38:51,439
Give it a try.

472
00:38:54,079 --> 00:38:56,760
Liu Lang is clever, but

473
00:38:56,760 --> 00:38:59,880
Mu Dan is busy with business
and can't teach you calligraphy every day.

474
00:38:59,880 --> 00:39:03,960
How about I find you a private tutor?

475
00:39:03,960 --> 00:39:08,840
I don't want any tutor,
having Mu Dan teach me is enough.

476
00:39:08,840 --> 00:39:14,319
I only like to cook, and I am not cut out
for studying and being an official.

477
00:39:14,920 --> 00:39:18,960
Liu Lang, becoming an official
is not the only path to succeed.

478
00:39:18,960 --> 00:39:23,039
If you like cooking,
I can hire a restaurant chef for you.

479
00:39:23,039 --> 00:39:27,840
Learn from him for a few years,
