I can take Liu Lang to visit him.

485
00:39:41,480 --> 00:39:43,280
No problem.

486
00:39:44,400 --> 00:39:49,639
Mu Dan, I've heard that Floral Envoy
enjoys painting for the beauties of Huanyun Tower.

487
00:39:49,639 --> 00:39:53,080
