491
00:40:10,039 --> 00:40:14,320
Liu Lang, you have to respect yourself.

492
00:40:14,320 --> 00:40:20,479
No matter what you want,
you must not belittle yourself, understand?

493
00:40:22,360 --> 00:40:24,160
Understood.

494
00:40:25,280 --> 00:40:27,480
Today I am available and in a good mood,

495
00:40:27,480 --> 00:40:30,080
so I will paint a picture.

496
00:40:35,679 --> 00:40:40,800
This painting is titled "Liu Lang Admiring
the Love of Mu Dan and Chang Yang".

497
00:40:40,800 --> 00:40:43,519
