498
00:40:43,519 --> 00:40:44,840
This is a painting technique.

499
00:40:44,840 --> 00:40:49,120
He's not in the painting, but actually
seeing the people in the painting.

500
00:40:49,920 --> 00:40:52,079
This painting is nice hanging here.

501
00:40:52,079 --> 00:40:56,280
All guests will know our deep affection then.

